quran[49]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif – Laam – Raa. Woi yε Nwoma no mu nsεm no bi, ne Qur’aan a ԑda adi pefee no"
  15,2,Mprε pii na wᴐn a wͻ’po nokorε no bεpε sε na anka wͻ’yε Muslimifoͻ
  15,3,"(Wodeε) gyae wͻn ma wͻ’nidi na wͻ’nye wͻn ani, na wͻ’ma anidaasoͻ hunu nye wͻn adaagyeε na ԑnkyԑ wͻ’behunu"
  15,4,"Kuro biara a Y’asεe no no, na εwͻ εberε a yahyε ato hͻ a yenim (sε yεde bεsεe no)"
  15,5,Ɛmma sε ͻman bi betumi ama ne berε (a ͻsεeε bεba ne soͻ no) aba animu anaa akͻ akyire
  15,6,"Deε wͻ’ka ne sε: “Wo a yasiane Afutusεm (Qur’aan) yi ama woͻ no, nokorε sε w’abͻ dam !”"
  15,7,"“Sε woka nokwafoͻ no ho ampa a, adεn nti na womma soro abͻfoͻ mma yεn hͻ?”"
  15,8,"Yε’mma soro abͻfoͻ nnsiane, gyesε nokorε bi nti, na sε (soro abͻfoͻ ba wͻn hͻ a), εno deε wͻ’nnya ahomegye berε"
  15,9,"Nokorε sε, Yεn na Ye’sianee (Qur’aan) Afutusεm no, na nokorε sε, Yεn na Yε’bεbͻ ho ban"
  15,10,"Ampa sε, Yε’somaa asomafoͻ dii w’anim kan kͻͻ tetefoͻ mmusua kuo no hͻ"
  15,11,Ͻsomafoͻ a ͻbaa wͻn hͻ biara no gyesε wͻ’di neho fεw
  15,12,Saa ara na Yε’ma (adwen bͻne) kͻwura abͻneεfoͻ no akoma mu
  15,13,"Wͻ’nnye (Qur’aan) no nni, abrԑ a ampa sε tetefoͻ no (a wͻ’annye annie no) mfatoho bi abetwam"
  15,14,Sε Yε’bue ͻsoro pono ma wͻn na wͻ’guso reforo kͻ mu mpo a
  15,15,"Nokorε sε anka wͻ’bεka sε: “Woi deε yaniso bri yεn. Daabi, yε’yε nnipa a yεde konya bi na anya yεn“"
  15,16,"Ampa sε, Y’ayε nsoromma (akεseε) wͻ soro, εna Y’ama ayε fε ama wͻn a wͻ’hwε"
  15,17,Ɛna Yε’bͻ ho ban fri ͻbonsam biara a yato no atwene (anaasε yapo no no nsam)
  15,18,Na mmom obia obewia (neho akͻ) tie no deε ogya frama pefee bedi n’akyi
  15,19,"Asaase nso Y’atrε mu εna Yε’de mmepͻ a esisi hͻ pintinn asisi soͻ, εna Yε’ma nneεma ahodoͻ pii a εyε dε fifiri wͻ soͻ"
  15,20,"Ɛna Y’ayε deε ehia wͻ asetena mu ama mo, ne wͻn nso a εnyε mo na mobͻ wͻn akͻnhoma"
  15,21,"Biribiara ho akoradeε wͻ Yεn hͻ, na Ye’siane no wͻ nhyehyεε a yenim so"
  15,22,"Ɛna Ye’soma mframa a εkayan (mununkum), na Y’asiane nsuo afri soro de ama mo anom aberε a εnyε mo na mokoraa (nsuo) no"
  15,23,"Nokorε sε, Yεn na yεma nkwa εna Yekum, na Yεn na (sε mowu kͻ a, Ye’si mo anan mu) di adeε"
  15,24,"Nokorε sε Ye’nim momu (awoͻ ntotoa soͻ) a wͻ’dii kan no, εna ampa nso sε Yenim wͻn a wͻ’di akyire no"
  15,25,"Nokorε sε, wo Wura Nyankopͻn, Ͻno na Ɔbεboa wͻn (nyinaa) ano (wͻ Atemmuda). Nokorε sε, Ɔne Onyansafoͻ, Ɔne Onimdefoͻ"
  15,26,"Nokorε sε, Yε’bͻͻ onipa fri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu"
  15,27,Ɛna Jinn no nso Yedii kan bͻͻ no fri ogya kεterεma mu (ansa na yεrebͻ onipa)
  15,28,"Kae εberε a wo Wura Nyankopͻn ka kyerεε Soro abͻfoͻ no sε: “Merebεbͻ onipa afri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu”"
  15,29,"“Enti sε Menwene no pεpεεpε wie na Mehome Mehonhom gu ne mu a, monfa moho nkͻ fͻm na monfa moanim mmutu fͻm ma no"
  15,30,Enti Soro abͻfoͻ no nyinaa bͻͻ mu de wͻn anim butuu fͻm (brεε wͻn ho ase) maa (Adam)
  15,31,"Gyesε Ibliis, wampene sε ͻbεka wͻn a wͻ’de wͻn anim butuu fͻm (brεε wͻn ho aseε) no ho"
  15,32,"Nyankopͻn kaa sε: “Ibliis, εdeεn na εha woͻ a w’annka wͻn a wͻ’de wͻn anim butuu fͻm no ho"
  15,33,"(Ibliis) kaa sε: “Menyε obi a mede m’anim bebutu fͻm ama onipa a Wobͻͻ no fri nεteε a awoͻ a εnee wͻ mu a efri atεkyε a yanwene mu”"
  15,34,"Onyankopͻn kaa sε: “Ɛneε fri ha kͻ, nokorε sε, yato wo atwene (afri Nyankopͻn ahummͻborͻ no mu)"
  15,35,"Nokorε sε, Onyankopͻn nnomee wͻ woso kͻpem Akatua Da no"
  15,36,"Ɔkaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, εneε na mame berε (anaasε enku me) kosi Da a yεbenyane awufoͻ no“"
  15,37,"Onyankopͻn kaa sε: “Woka wͻn a yama wͻn εberε no ho"
  15,38,Kͻpem Dͻnhwere no a yenim“
  15,39,"(Ibliis) kaa sε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, sεdeε W’ama me ayera yi deε, nokorε sε, mεma (bͻne) ayε wͻn fε wͻ asaase so, na m’ayera wͻn nyinaa"
  15,40,Gyesε Wonkoa a wͻ’di nokorε a wͻn wͻ wͻn mu no “
  15,41,"Onyankopͻn kaa sε: “Woi ne kwan tenenee a εwͻ Menkyεn no “"
  15,42,"“Nokorε sε, Menkoa no deε wonni tumi wͻ wͻn so, gyesε ayerafoͻ no a wͻ’bedi w’akyi no"
  15,43,"Nokorε sε, Amanehunu gya no ne bea a yεde ahyε wͻn nyinaa bͻ"
  15,44,"(Amanehunu gya no) wͻ apono nson, na εpono no mu biara wͻ (abͻneεfoͻ) sononko a yakyekyε (ama wͻn)"
  15,45,"Nokorε sε, Nyame-surofoͻ no wͻ Soro aheman a nsuo aniwa wͻ mu no mu"
  15,46,"(Yεbεka akyerε wͻn sε): “Monfa Asomdweε ne abotͻyεmu nwura mu”"
  15,47,"Yebeyi ͻyaw die afri wͻn akoma mu ama wͻn atena onua dͻ mu, ahwε wͻn ho wͻn ho anim wͻ ahennwa so"
  15,48,"Ɔberε biara nto wͻn, na yεmma wͻn mfri mu nso da"
  15,49,"(Nkͻmhyεni), bͻ Menkoa no amaneε sε, nokorε Mene Bͻnefakyε Hene no, na Me ara nso Mene Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no"